&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Provide leadership in all areas affecting Research Finance; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;operational management for sponsored program post-award administration, management and grant accounting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
